   "body" : "This adds a SHA512 hash of the resulting merged tree to merge commit messages. This may or may not make SHA1 collision attacks harder (since the GPG signatures sign a SHA1 hash of the commit's contents, this is not a final solution at all).\r\n\r\nThe hash can be verified by running `git ls-tree --full-tree -r --name-only HEAD | LANG=C sort | xargs -n 1 sha512sum | sha512sum` in the repository root.",
